query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(mk ci) NoHashJoin(ci mk n) NoMergeJoin(ci mk n t) NoHashJoin(ci mk n t k) */ select min(k.keyword) AS movie_keyword,
min(n.name) AS actor_name,
min(t.title) AS hero_movie
from movie_keyword AS mk
inner join cast_info AS ci
on ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
inner join name AS n
on n.id = ci.person_id
inner join title AS t
on t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.production_year > 1999
inner join keyword AS k
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('hospital',
'female-nudity',
'fight',
'tv-special',
'fight',
'tv-special',
'laser',
'blood');
